window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Telorans just got pummeled in Meligorn space, but the victory came with unexpectedly bad news: there is another Teloran fleet heading in their direction. </b></p> <p>What will the Federation Navy decide to do? </p> <p>On Earth, Stephanie's plans to help rebuild are slowly taking shape. Will her team be able to figure out a plan to reduce the toxic radiation zones, or will they die of radiation sickness or magical destruction and sink the future of the planet? </p> <p>Regardless of the victories, some in power are willing to make deals to try and cut Stephanie and her team out of the future. But she is a Morgana. There are no other alternatives, no matter the risk to her and her team.</p>"; 
